Tasmota:
	SetOption59 1    # Für switches Verhalten in Homeassist

	TV: Um =00:30 wenn Energieaufnahme<70W --> Schalte aus
            rule1 on Time#Minute=30 do rule2 1 endon
            rule2 on Energy#Power<70 do backlog power off; rule2 0 endon

	Umwälzpumpe:
            rule1 on Ds18s20#Temperature<50 do power off endon on Ds18s20#Temperature>55 do power on endon
